# TodoMVC demo workflow
goto https://demo.playwright.dev/todomvc
localstorage-clear
goto https://demo.playwright.dev/todomvc
fill "What needs to be done?" "Buy groceries"
press Enter
fill "What needs to be done?" "Walk the dog"
press Enter
fill "What needs to be done?" "Read a book"
press Enter
check checkbox "Toggle Todo" --nth 1
click "Active"
verify-text "Buy groceries"
verify-text "Read a book"
verify-no-text "Walk the dog"
 